    ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                               
    DATA DIVISION.                                      
    LINKAGE SECTION.                                    
  01 LS-VARS.                                           
     05   LS-LENGTH PIC 99 BINARY.                      
          05   LS-A      PIC 9(1).               
     05   LS-B      PIC 9(1).               
     05   LS-C      PIC 9(2).               
    PROCEDURE DIVISION USING LS-VARS.       
         DISPLAY "LS-A  "  LS-A.            
         DISPLAY "LS-B  "  LS-B.            
         DISPLAY "LS-C  "  LS-C.            
         COMPUTE LS-C = LS-A + LS-B.        
         DISPLAY "LS-A  "  LS-A.            
         DISPLAY "LS-B  "  LS-B.            
         DISPLAY "LS-C  "  LS-C.            
               GOBACK.                      
